Examples:
  helm create microservices
  helm install my-micro charts/microservices -n demo --create-namespace
  helm upgrade my-micro charts/microservices -n demo
  helm uninstall my-micro -n demo

Options:
  -f                   Specify values.yaml file
  -n                   Specify namespace
  -A                   List releases across all namespaces
  --create-namespace   Create specified namespace when installing chart

Common commands:
  helm repo add https://charts.bitnami.com/bitnami         Adds the Bitnami chart repository to Helm's local list of chart repositories
  helm search bitnami/postgresql --versions                Searches for available charts within the Bitnami repository for PostgreSQL
  helm pull                              Downloads the PostgreSQL chart locally
  helm show values <helm_chart>          Displays the default values used by the chart
  helm install                           Installs the PostgreSQL chart into a Kubernetes cluster
  helm upgrade                           Upgrades the deployed PostgreSQL release to a newer chart version
  helm rollback                          Rolls back the PostgreSQL release to a previous version
  helm list                              Lists Helm releases deployed in the Kubernetes cluster
  helm get values                        Retrieves the values used for the deployed release
  helm get manifests                     Shows the Kubernetes manifests of the deployed release

OCI Registry usage commands:
  helm registry login registry-1.docker.io                                               Login to OCI registry (Use your dockerhub username and password)
  oras repo tags registry-1.docker.io/twilight4/movie-api                                Searches for tags in an OCI-compliant registry
  helm package ./<CHART_NAME>                                                            Bundle helm chart as a .tgz OCI image
  helm push <ARCHIVED_DIR> oci://registry-1.docker.io/twilight4                          Push the helm chart to an oci registry
  helm pull oci://registry-1.docker.io/<USERNAME>/<CHART_NAME> --version=<VERSION>       Pull movie-review chart from Dockerhub repository
  tar -xzf movie-review-<VERSION>.tgz                                                    Untar movie-review chart
  helm show values oci://registry-1.docker.io/<USERNAME>/<CHART_NAME> --version 0.1.0    Show values for PostgreSQL chart

Repository:
  helm repo add <repository_name>          Add a new helm repository
  helm repo list/ls                        List chart repositories
  helm repo remove                         Remove one or more chart repositories
  helm repo update                         Update information of available charts locally from chart repositories
  helm repo remove <repository_name>       Delete a helm repository

Helm charts management:
  helm install <chart_name>                Install a helm chart
  helm upgrade <chart_name>                Ugprade a helm chart
  helm upgrade --install <chart_name>      Ugprade a helm chart (manage the existing resources instead of creating duplicates)
  helm rollback <chart_name>               Rollback a helm chart
  helm uninstall <release_name>            Uninstall a helm chart

Misc:
  helm status <release>                    Get status of a release
  helm search <chart_name>                 Search the available chart using the search command
  helm create <chart_name>                 Create a helm chart
  helm get <chart_release_name>            Download helm chart as a tar archive
  helm dependency update                   Update helm dependencies
